label: landParcelID
comment: The ULPIN(Unique Land Parcel Identification Number) representing the land parcel corresponding to the observation.

label: surveyNumber
comment: The unique land survey number allocated to the land corresponding to this observation.

label: baseSurveyNumber
comment: The base survey number of the land corresponding to this observation.

label: subdivisionNumber
comment: The subdivision number from the land survey number corresponding to this observation
